OOC: sorry Yanshosh about cutting out of the convo so soon, my computer 
crashed and i had to reinstall AOL.

    Aracnia looked to the group around Kitkats base. It was Megatrons 
goons....the expendable team as she recalled. Now that they were all 
assembled, they could get on with the mission.

    Megatron turned to Kitkat, "I belive I asked you a question.....and also, 
what is this I hear about a clone of myself running around on board?"
